{"id": 57, "ts": 1778800243.8159056, "event": "public_discussion_message", "round": 2, "agent": "agent_3", "message": "After reviewing all available attributes for each candidate, the balance of strengths and weaknesses points most clearly to Candidate\u202fC.\n**Strengths:** 100\u202f% reliability, calmness in crises, rapid correct decision\u2011making, excellent attention to detail, solid technical understanding, and\u2014importantly\u2014demonstrated ability to create a positive atmosphere and put concern for others above everything, which indicates effective teamwork on long\u2011haul flights.\n**Weaknesses:** difficulty communicating ideas, an egocentric attitude, and limited willingness for further education. While these are concerns, they are less likely to jeopardize immediate crew coordination than the overt hostility and uncooperativeness shown by Candidate\u202fB, or the lack of any teamwork evidence for Candidates\u202fA and\u202fD, both of whom also have additional personal or temperamental issues.\nGiven the critical need for reliability, sound judgment under pressure, and especially smooth crew interaction on long\u2011distance routes, Candidate\u202fC offers the strongest overall fit.\n**My vote:** Candidate C\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
